State of NC, Dept. of Sec. of State 134P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Ronald Thompson Corbett, for Corbett, Ronald Thompson. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC, Dept. of Sec. of State.
